OL,3,CCouncil aims to tackle decline in
OL,4,Cshoppers using Douglas high street
OL,6,FThe number of people visiting the Isle
OL,7,Fof Man's capital for shopping has
OL,8,Fdropped by more than 10% - with nearly
OL,9,Ftwo thirds revealing they leave the
OL,10,Fisland for leisure reasons.
OL,12,FA recent survey found there had been a
OL,13,Fsignificant drop in the number of
OL,14,Fpeople visiting Douglas city centre -
OL,15,Fwith those visiting Strand Street
OL,16,Fdecreasing by more than a million - or
OL,17,F12.5% - since 2019.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
