OL,3,CCouncil aims to tackle decline in
OL,4,Cshoppers using Douglas high street
OL,6,FTerry's Tatos opened in Strand Street
OL,7,Fat the beginning of 2023, and while it
OL,8,Fis in a 'stable place', they say it is
OL,9,Fa tough time for small businesses on
OL,10,Fthe island.
OL,12,FManager Rachel Marsland said: "It is
OL,13,Freally really tricky, I'm not gonna
OL,14,Flie. Unfortunately (there's) rising
OL,15,Fcosts and things like that. We're
OL,16,Fdoing alright but yes, we'll get
OL,17,Fthere."
OL,26,@vD@TpmvD@\pn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
