CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773857158
OL,3,CCouncil aims to tackle decline in
OL,4,Cshoppers using Douglas high street
OL,6,FThe survey also suggested 63% of
OL,7,Fshoppers often leave the island for
OL,8,Fshopping and leisure purposes, due to
OL,9,Fthe wider variety off the island.
OL,11,FIt is an impact felt by smaller
OL,12,Fbusinesses within Douglas with some
OL,13,Fconcern from shoppers, as some
OL,14,Fdescribed the high street as an
OL,15,F'essential' part of island life.
OL,17,FRegular customers at Terry's Tatos
OL,18,Fsaid it is integral to the community.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
