CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773857158
OL,3,CCouncil aims to tackle decline in
OL,4,Cshoppers using Douglas high street
OL,6,FScott said: "A lot of people will come
OL,7,Fin here regularly, and we'll get to
OL,8,Fknow each other, so you build up a
OL,9,Fcommunity."
OL,11,FOwen added: "You've got to support
OL,12,Flocal, otherwise places will be shut
OL,13,Fdown and you won't be able to go
OL,14,Fanywhere."
OL,16,FTerry's Tatos also been recently
OL,17,Fvisited by some of the island's newest
OL,18,Fresidents, with TV's Noel Edmunds and
OL,19,Fboxer Tyson Fury stopping by for a
OL,20,Fvisit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
