PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773857158
OL,3,CCouncil aims to tackle decline in
OL,4,Cshoppers using Douglas high street
OL,6,F"It was the most amazing experience,
OL,7,Fas you can imagine", Rachel said.
OL,9,F"We recently had Tyson and Paris Fury,
OL,10,Falong with their children, so there
OL,11,Fwas the nine of them in here. They are
OL,12,Fabsolutely wonderful people - the
OL,13,Fchildren were really well behaved - it
OL,14,Fwas really nice and Tyson was saying
OL,15,F'how's it going?' with it being tough
OL,16,Ftimes at the moment."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
