CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773857158
OL,3,CCouncil aims to tackle decline in
OL,4,Cshoppers using Douglas high street
OL,6,FOliver Cheshire works for Douglas City
OL,7,FCouncil, and says while bringing
OL,8,Fpeople to the high street is a
OL,9,Fchallenge, it's a 'global issue' being
OL,10,Ftackled after the rise of online
OL,11,Fshopping.
OL,13,FHe said: "It's so easy just to stay at
OL,14,Fhome and shop online. It's the
OL,15,Fconvenience of it. So yeah, it's it's
OL,16,Fdefinitely had, a big impact."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
