FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773857158
OL,3,CCouncil aims to tackle decline in
OL,4,Cshoppers using Douglas high street
OL,6,FWhen asked if he was concerned about
OL,7,Fthe number of people wishing to travel
OL,8,Foff-island for shops, he said: "I
OL,9,Fthink it's just the nature of being on
OL,10,Fan island.
OL,12,F"Obviously it would be nice to have
OL,13,Fthose bigger brands here, but then you
OL,14,Fcould argue when you've got those sort
OL,15,Fof brands, then it's it's like an
OL,16,Fecosystem, it can affect then the
OL,17,Ftrade at other smaller businesses as
OL,18,Fwell."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
