PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773857158
OL,3,CCouncil aims to tackle decline in
OL,4,Cshoppers using Douglas high street
OL,6,FThe council say free weekend parking
OL,7,Fis coming to Shaw's Brow car park from
OL,8,FApril, in an attempt to encourage more
OL,9,Fpeople to visit the capital.
OL,11,FCouncil Leader, Devon Watson,
OL,12,Fexplained: 'We asked the public, both
OL,13,Fresidents and businesses, what would
OL,14,Fencourage them to visit Douglas more
OL,15,Foften.
OL,17,F"Parking was clearly the main issue so
OL,18,Fwe have listened carefully and taken
OL,19,Faction where we can.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
