PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773857158
OL,3,CCouncil aims to tackle decline in
OL,4,Cshoppers using Douglas high street
OL,6,F"All in all, we hope this initiative
OL,7,Fwill boost footfall, strengthen trade
OL,8,Fand make it even easier for people to
OL,9,Fenjoy everything our city centre has
OL,10,Fto offer."
OL,12,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,13,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,14,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,15,Four region.
